full_text: Today‚Äôs new CDC numbers on autism regrettably show a greater prevalence‚Äîup 20% in NJ to 1 in 34 kids.  This quantifying of prevalence of autism‚Äîmandated by my legislation‚Äîhelps us fight for & secure much-needed fed support for treatment & education of children w/ autism.
